{extends file='MobileTemplates/master.tpl'}
{block name='main-content'}
	<div class="content">
		<section class="main">
			<div class="detail-page">
				<h2 class="main-title">Work in Japan</h2>
				<div class="container">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-xs-12">
							<p>We suggest you using Job Board to find job.<br>
								We are always gathering recruit information for someone who lives in Japan.<br>
								Also ,We want support someone who will come Japan to find job. </p>
							<p>Many client post Job offer.<br>
								They require Restaurant stuff, Shop stuff ,Language teacher, Office worker, Event stuff, and the others.<br>
								There are many offers therefore, you can find what you want.</p>
							<p>You can choice employment style on this web site.<br>
								If you want to work whole day, you will choice “full time job”.<br>
								You can work short time, if you entry part time job.Also you can work as freelancer.</p>
							<p>We wish you will find good jobs in Japn.</p>
							<h4>How you to get job in Japan</h4>
							<h3>*Check your VISA</h3>
							<div class="box-gray">
								<p>If you want to work in Japan.There are many types.<br>
									You had better to check if your VISA meet the requirements or not at web site of immigration bureau of Japan.</p>
							</div>
							<h3>*How to write Curriculum Vitae as RIREKISHO</h3>
							<div class="box-gray">
								<p>Next step, you have to writ Curriculum Vitae as RIREKISHO.<br>
									I'm gonna show you few tips to adjust RIREKISHO.</p>
							</div>
							<ul class="list-number">
								<li>If you are male, shave mustache.</li>
								<li>Cut your hair.</li>
								<li>take a picture, with suits& tie.</li>
							</ul>
							<h3>*Get“INKAN”</h3>
							<div class="box-gray">
								<p>In japan, everybody use INKAN as a signature on official documents.<br>
									INKAN is small stump.It may cost 2000~3000YEN.<br>
									You may require INKAN when you are employed.</p>
							</div>
							<h3>*Make BANK account</h3>
							<div class="box-gray">
								<p>Bank account is necessary to get your wages.<br>
									Some employer require you specific bank to reduce transfer fee.<br>
									However, there is possibility that the bank refuse to open your account unless you have suitable reasons; such as salary deposit.<br>
									If you are having trouble with opening a bank account, contact the bank and your employer.</p>
							</div>
							<h3>*find job</h3>
							<div class="box-gray">
								<p>I recommend you to use job board. Because there are many offers.<br>
									Another way, Using “Employment service center for foreigners” is better way to find job.<br>
									These are in TOKYO,NAGOYA,and Osaka.<br>
									You can search job at these centers. Also you can join the job seminar at here.<br>
									You can find it if you use internet, and search “Employment service center for foreigners”.<br>
									Then you can find web site.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
{/block}